title: 8.1.6.2.1.2.1 CDP Physical Credential Authentication Unfreeze Request Data

content.text:
Figure 634 specifies the Request Data for a Personality Unfreeze Request operation using Physical
Credential Authentication (refer to the AUS field in Figure 285).

tables.title: Table_8_1_6_2_1_2_1_CDP_Physical_Credential_Authentication_Unfreeze_Request_Data
tables.table_md:
| Bytes | Description | |:---|:---| | 05:00 | CDP Request Data Frame Common Fields (CDPREQDFCF): This field contains the CDP Request Data Frame common fields (refer to Figure 630). This field shall be set to the CDP Response Data Frame common fields with the CDP Request Message Type field set to a value of 1h (i.e., Personality Unfreeze Request). | | 06 | Personality Identifier (PERID): This field specifies the Personality Identifier this operation is targeting (refer to Figure 447). | | 07 | CDP Authentication Method Identifier value of 01h (CDPAMI): This field specifies the CDP Authentication Method Identifier value of 01h (refer to the AUS field in Figure 285). | | (08+REQDS-3):08 | Credential Value (CREDV): This field specifies the value of the credential.
The value of this field is the Physical Presence Indicator (PPI) (refer to section 5.2.26.1.24.1.1). |
